                    "description": "From July 1st 2013 until June 2014 I was assigned as an equipment engineer Illumination and Projection to the NXE source project. At this project I was responsible with my colleagues to introduce and support this new technology at our customers with focus on availalbility and serviceability. From July 1st 2014 I left ASML to start my own business.",
